data.meta_description:
1,053 likes, 36 comments - sarahsophief on November 13, 2022: "There’s just something about this song! 

Woody Guthrie wrote “All You Fascists Bound To Lose” in the 1940’s. We (@resistancerevivalchorus ) sang it outside *rump tower before the 2020 election . We sang it last night with @rhiannongiddens last night….. and then we held the SENATE!!! 

These fascists are bound to keep losing! 

Let’s go @raphaelwarnock in the Georgia runoff!!! 

Via @steve_vladeck on why this is a big deal (especially if Warnock wins):

Three huge differences between a 50-50 and 51-49 D majority:

1) Having a majority on each Committee versus power sharing/deadlocks requiring discharge petitions;

2) No single D Senator can hijack/block nominations; and

3) Ds can have *two* members absent and still hold votes.

#stayhuman #keepshowingup".
